data.title: What is the difference between Smith and Wellesley?
data.meta_description: Answer (1 of 4): I went to Wellesley and it was a great yet challenging opportunity. Having applied to and been accepted to Bryn Mawr and Mt. Holyoke as well, I chose the school based on statistics and not on my feelings that I would fit in or enjoy the school. I really wanted to attend Bryn Mawr...
